      "proof": "Set u=a*u_A+b*u_B. Then L*u=24a*e_A+24b*e_B and u is nonnegative, so u algebraically stabilizes back to all-3. Least action gives the true odometer v<=u. For w=u-v>=0, final stability implies L*w<=0; the sink-connected reduced-Laplacian maximum principle forces w=0. Thus v=u exactly."
